query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-tablayout',
'binaryfiles',
'dijkstra',
'distributed',
'dynamics-ax-2012',
'getline',
'kml',
'libxml2',
'matching',
'normalization',
'pyramid',
'stm32',
'vi');
